gnized by Olmstead et al. (1992, 1993), based on rbcL sequences with strong support, and has been inferred in analyses of 18S rDNA (Albach et al., 2001) and many subsequent molecular studies (e.g., Olmstead et al., 2000; Savolainen et al., 2000; Soltis et al, 2000; Albach et al., 2001; Bremer et al., 2002; Hilu et al., 2003).\n',1,'ICBN','A. L. Takhtajan ','node-based_crown_clade_branch-modified','The least inclusive clade containing Lamium purpureum Linnaeus 1753 (Lamiales), Solanum nigrum Linnaeus 1753 (Solanales), Gentiana procera T. Holm 1901 (Gentianales), Borago officinalis Linnaeus 1753 (Boraginaceae), and Vahlia capensis (Linnaeus f.) Thunberg 1782 (Vahliaceae).  This is a node-based definition in which all of the specifiers are extant; it is intended to apply to a crown clade.  Abbreviated definition: < Lamium purpureum Linnaeus 1753 & Solanum nigrum Linnaeus 1753 & Gentiana procera T. Holm 1901 & Borago officinalis Linnaeus 1753 & Vahlia capensis (Linnaeus f.) Thunberg 1782.','--- !map:ActiveSupport::HashWithIndifferentAccess \nphylogeny: !map:ActiveSupport::HashWithIndifferentAccess \n  \"0\": !map:ActiveSupport::HashWithIndifferentAccess \n    citation_authors: Olmstead, R. G., K. Kim, R. K. Jansen, and S. J. Wagstaff\n    journal: Mol. Phylogenet. Evol.\n    figure: \"\"\n    year: \"2000\"\n    volume: \"16\"\n    number: \"\"\n    pages: \"96\\xE2\\x80\\x93112\"\n    keywords: \"\"\n    isbn: \"\"\n    url: \"\"\n    doi: \"\"\n    treebase_tree_id: \"\"\n    citation_type: journal\n    title: The phylogeny of the Asteridae sensu lato based on chloroplast ndhF gene sequences.\n  \"1\": !map:ActiveSupport::HashWithIndifferentAccess \n    citation_authors: Soltis, D. E., P. S. Soltis, M. W. Chase, M. E. Mort, D. C. Albach, M. Zanis, V. Savolainen, W. H., Hahn, S. B., Hoot, M. F., Fay, M., Axtell, S. M., Swensen, L. M., Prince, W. J., Kress, K. C. Nixon, and J. S. Farris\n    journal: Bot. J. Linn. Soc.\n    figure: \"\"\n    year: \"2000\"\n    volume: 